s by massive AGBs, but are also compatible with the\nproduction of second generation elements (like Na) and low Li produced by, for\nexample, fast rotating massive stars.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 11 Aug 2016 17:32:06 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-26"}
