 distribution, the mean occupation\nfunction, and the velocity distribution of satellite galaxies inside halos. The\nresults suggest that galaxy 3PCFs can further help constrain the above\ngalaxy-halo relation and test theoretical models.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2016 02:24:24 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-10-26"}
