h can be used to\ndetect many elements in the structure group of a closed oriented topological\nmanifold, even when the fundamental group of the manifold is torsion free. In\nparticular, we apply this homological higher rho invariant to show that the\nstructure group is not finitely generated for a class of manifolds.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 12 Aug 2016 02:32:26 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 5 Oct 2016 18:46:44 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Wed, 28 Jun 2017 14:58:43 GMT"},{"version":"v4","created":"Wed, 9 Jan 2019 03:59:45 GMT"},{"version":"v5","created":"Mon, 24 Feb 2020 16:54:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-02-25"}
